{"tid":2459152,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Apink鄭恩地只穿內衣對鏡自拍 炸出超狂馬甲線辣翻","createTime":"2021-03-24T03:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T08:38:37.000Z","uid":9573,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c479c735d64cf4e5e45f2d316f1eba691dfde6ad","tid":2459152,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:44:38.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣女團Apink，日前為慶祝出道10周年紀念，特別開設線上展覽會《Pink Carnival》及線上快閃店，與粉絲們一同狂歡，掀起熱烈討論。人氣成員鄭恩地(정은지)，今日(3/23)也在個人社群媒體上曬出健身近況，精實的好身材令粉絲們驚艷不已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2021-03-23/1024/20210323002591.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2021-03-23%2F1024%2F20210323002591.jpg&h=cd825593&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭恩地近日在IG上曬出健身成效，秀出超狂的腹肌立即吸引目光。<br />\n<br />\n鄭恩地自女團Apink身份出道後，便以極具爆發力的嗓音及甜美的臉蛋受到大批粉絲的喜愛，但她也因微肉的棉花糖身材遭到酸民猛烈攻擊，近幾年她除了靠著嚴格控制飲食成功瘦身外，也積極健身雕塑身材，同時整合熒幕指紋解鎖，更大方在YouTube頻道及IG上分享健身資訊與減肥過程，吸引超過214萬人追蹤。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.muji.net/img/item/4550182146615_1260.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.muji.net%2Fimg%2Fitem%2F4550182146615_1260.jpg&h=8c7c85dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恩地因微肉的棉花糖身材遭到酸民猛烈攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n近日，鄭恩地再度曬出健身時的照片，只見她穿著黑色運動內衣及同款運動長褲，與教練一同對著鏡子拍攝各種角度，大方秀出苦練許久的川字腹肌與身材曲線，內置8GB RAM及256GB儲存容量，令粉絲們看了忍不住大讚「哇~這線條太好看了」、「11字腹肌太帥了」、「實在太狂，姊姊超帥的」，吸引超過9萬人按讚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/73554700_2530826687030678_1144915406394228736_o.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=hGL3hGQ9X6sAX-lIZFC&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=ca1acf1f53fcfa3f2de167f27b5eb2bd&amp;oe=6080F0CD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F73554700_2530826687030678_1144915406394228736_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26ccb%3D1-3%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DhGL3hGQ9X6sAX-lIZFC%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3Dca1acf1f53fcfa3f2de167f27b5eb2bd%26oe%3D6080F0CD&h=bd59ddc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粉絲們看了忍不住大讚。<br />\n<br />\n鄭恩地出道多年不僅會唱、會跳，還會演戲與主持，去年7月發行SOLO迷你專輯《Simple》獲得好評後，她所主持的廣播節目《鄭恩地的歌謠廣場》也在2020年度韓國品牌大賞上榮獲「最佳廣播DJ獎」。鄭恩地今年更與金秀美、朴明秀、Hani、前進等人，一同演出真人秀節目《秀美山莊》，播出後話題不斷，規格效能更進一步，人氣再度大爆發。"},{"pid":"abe632667ef26bef03930186617f3c72a0b20d0f","tid":2459152,"uid":78856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:45:17.000Z","msg":"8GB ram"},{"pid":"54454ce01831e47f283814880241cd933aa09905","tid":2459152,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"仲撈緊？"},{"pid":"3256bfebba868fbf74519642ab4efe3b24f68722","tid":2459152,"uid":342887,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:47:30.000Z","msg":"內置8GB RAM及256GB儲存容量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb4f8500b0e241163514b820e67b79bbc262e35","tid":2459152,"uid":3718,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:50:01.000Z","msg":"同時整合熒幕指紋解鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee29316eab88eef5a04ec63ced32dc17bd81f65","tid":2459152,"uid":11644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:55:59.000Z","msg":"好耐無見樓豬了"},{"pid":"421d8a8ad361b4ee471041d7dadf04d58c15661e","tid":2459152,"uid":34241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:49:50.000Z","msg":"你求其都貼張內衣圖出黎hea下我都好丫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb73e37e74ee963d1d85ed7f9cea69726edaeb3","tid":2459152,"uid":327880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T08:38:37.000Z","msg":"最尾張相&hellip;&hellip;朱千雪嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}